patch_ops.value: No spontaneous/gaze nystagmus. Normal tracking, saccades, and OKN. Dix-Hallpike negative. Caloric irrigations within normal limits despite a relative reduction. Fixation suppression was successful.

Slightly decreased VOR gain with normal symmetry and phase. Step velocity time constants normal. Optokinetic nystagmus was symmetric and within normal limits. Visual-vestibular fixation suppression was intact.
